{
  "stem": "15396.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was living with a woman named Beatrice Cartwright, who had a beautiful yacht.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went there to see if I could maybe get them to help us with this project, which was pretty crackpot idea anyway.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Beatrice said to me, oh, I looked terrible cause I hadn't had a bath and shave and all this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I went and took a shower and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew him quite well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so when Freddie came on board, I said-- we were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we walked out on the deck, and I told him what we wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And suddenly he had a nervous breakdown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, get off the ship, you get off the boat, you're going to get me in trouble and all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, they heard this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People on the docks heard it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And needless to say, I got off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we had-- we had a few things-- plans to do things that didn't work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's why when I started working for Fry, actually you had to have-- he had to have somebody there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had-- still had remnants of my-- of my ambulance driver's uniform because it's all the clothes I had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it looked a little bit impressive to the refugees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And at one point, some of them, they were trying-- you didn't know who was trying to get in, whether they were real refugees or not.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was supposed to stand there at the head of the stairs and try and keep a little bit of order.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was my first job there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then I started delivering papers, your false papers, and taking people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
